Name: Average time to reach 'Completed + Cancelled' from 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000158FAB73550> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total number of transitions from 'Completed + Cancelled' to any other activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average time before 'Completed + Cancelled' occurs after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Time from the start of the case to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average waiting time before 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Longest time between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Completed + Closed' across cases
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Shortest time to 'Completed + Cancelled' from case start in the event log
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to 'Completed + In Call' in cases where both occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
